      • judge

        public static InstinctResult judge(java.lang.String appId,
                                   java.lang.String instinctCall)
                            throws InstinctServiceException,
                                   MalFormedApplicationException
        This method sends an online request to the Instinct server to judge the application from omni system.
        Parameters:
        appId - application id to judge.
        instinctCall - supports "preCheck" and "finalCheck" online judge.
        Returns:
        InstinctResult indicating judging result from Instinct server.
        Throws:
        InstinctServiceException - Instinct server exception.
        MalFormedApplicationException - omni application exception.
        See Also:
        InstinctResult
